<?xml version="1.0"?>
<!--

This document descide the parameters of the menu.
Without the infomenu no menu will be displayed. Some informations are obligatory:
    - the nbr of buttons. They need to fit with the nbrs of button (or to be superior).
Here is the template of the document:

<root>
    <infomenu>
        <nbrbutton></nbrbutton>  -> (int) number of buttons in the menu (without buttons in dropdown)
        <icone></icone> ->  (string) fas icone name
        <iconetext></iconetext> -> (string) svg next to the icone
    </infomenu>
            1. Template menu with dropdown:
    <buttonx> where x >= 0 && x < nbrbutton
        <dropdownnbr></dropdown>
        <text>Boutton1<text>  -> (string) text to display over the button
        <href></href>
        <icone>fas icone name</icone>
        <dropdownx>
            <textdrop></textdrop> -> (string) text to display over the dropdownbutton
            <hrefdrop></hrefdrop> -> (string) link of the button
        </dropdownx> where x >= 0 && x < dropdownnbr
    </buttonx>
            2. Template menu without dropdown
    <buttonx> where x >= 0 && x < nbrbutton
        <dropdownnbr>0</dropdown>
        <icone>fas icone name</icone>
        <text></text> -> (string) text to display over the button
        <href></href> -> (string) link of the button
    </buttonx>

-->

<root>
